title: Stefon Diggs Interview, Week 1 Overreactions (Football 09/13)
description:
As the dust settles from Week 1 in the NFL, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora react to some of Will Brinson's overreactions from around the league. Are the Colts the worst team in the NFL? (2:20), Can Jared Goff and the Rams win the NFC West? (4:42), How much will the Seahawks o-line woes hurt them? (8:50), How concerned should we be about J.J. Watt? (14:00), Jaguars the best team in the AFC South? (16:00), Will Kareem Hunt be the best rookie RB this season? (18:45). Then Minnesota Vikings WR Stefon Diggs joins the podcast (29:55-37:30) to discuss his big time performance on MNF, Minnesota's improved offensive line, how good Dalvin Cook can be and much more.
